    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require all SIA licence holders to complete any new training standards",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "The government should make it a legal requirement for all SIA licence holders to complete new training standards if new ones are introduced, not when their licence expires. Without this law, outdated training could be followed for a maximum of 3 years before having to complete the new standard.",
